description:
Features

This heavy-duty battery switch is designed to provide reliable and convenient control over your 12-48V battery system. With its waterproof construction and robust design, it's ideal for demanding applications in vehicles and off-road equipment.

  • Waterproof Design: The A70F Battery Switch is built to withstand harsh weather conditions and keep your electrical connections protected from moisture.
  • Heavy-Duty Construction: Durable materials ensure long-lasting performance even under demanding conditions.
  • 12-48V Compatibility: Designed to work with a wide range of battery systems, making it versatile for various applications.
  • Power-Cut Functionality: Easily isolate your battery from the electrical system when needed, preventing accidental discharge or drain.
  • Master-Switch Disconnect Isolator: Provides complete control over power flow to and from your batteries.

Specifications

The A70F Battery Switch is built with robust specifications for reliable performance:

  • Voltage Range: 12-48V
  • Current Rating: High enough to handle the demands of most automotive and off-road applications.
  • Waterproof Rating: Designed to meet or exceed industry standards for water resistance.
  • Terminal Type: Secure and reliable connections for optimal power transfer.

Benefits

This heavy-duty battery switch offers a range of benefits for your vehicle or equipment:

  • Enhanced Safety: Isolate your battery to prevent accidental discharges and protect your electrical system.
  • Increased Battery Life: Reduce parasitic drain on your batteries when the vehicle is not in use.
  • Convenient Power Management: Easily disconnect and reconnect your battery for maintenance or storage.
  • Improved Security: Prevent unauthorized access to your vehicle's electrical system.

Usage

The A70F Battery Switch is easy to install and use:

1. Connect the switch to your battery according to the provided instructions. 2. Use the switch lever to turn power on or off. The "ON" position allows current to flow through the circuit, while the "OFF" position isolates the battery from the electrical system.

3. Remember to always disconnect the battery before working on your vehicle's electrical system.

titre: 2 Pack For RV Roof Vent Seal 51" TPE Rubber Camper Vent Fan Gasket Replacement Caravan Exterior Waterproofing Accessories
description:
Features

This 2-pack offers durable and effective sealing for your RV roof vents. Crafted from high-quality TPE rubber, these gaskets are designed to provide a reliable barrier against water intrusion, keeping your camper dry and comfortable.

  • TPE Rubber Construction: TPE (Thermoplastic Elastomer) is known for its flexibility, durability, and resistance to weathering and temperature extremes, ensuring long-lasting performance.
  • Waterproof Protection: The gaskets effectively seal around your RV vent fan, preventing water leaks and keeping your camper dry even in heavy rain or humid conditions.
  • Universal Fit: 51" Length: These gaskets are designed to fit a wide range of RV roof vents with a circumference of up to 51 inches.

Specifications

Each gasket in this pack measures 51 inches in length, providing ample coverage for most standard RV vent fan openings.

Benefits

Investing in these RV roof vent seal gaskets offers numerous benefits:

  • Prevent Water Damage: Keep your camper dry and protected from costly water damage caused by leaks.
  • Improve Comfort: Enjoy a more comfortable living environment free from moisture and dampness.
  • Extend the Life of Your RV: Protect your RV's structure and components from the damaging effects of water intrusion.

Usage

Replacing your RV roof vent gaskets is a straightforward process:

  1. Carefully remove the old gasket from your vent fan.
  2. Clean the vent flange thoroughly to ensure a secure bond for the new gasket.

titre: New 12V - 48V Selector 2 Position On-off Power Switch 300A Battery Disconnect Cut Off Kill Switch For Car Vehicle RV Marine Boat
description:
Features

This heavy-duty power switch is designed to provide reliable on/off control for your 12V or 48V battery system. Its dual position design allows you to easily select between two voltage settings, making it perfect for vehicles with multiple battery configurations.

  • Two-position selector switch: Easily toggle between 12V and 48V power outputs
  • High current capacity: Handles up to 300 amps of current, suitable for demanding applications
  • Durable construction: Built to withstand harsh conditions and provide long-lasting performance
  • Waterproof design: Protects against moisture and damage from the elements

Specifications

Voltage Selector: 12V - 48V

Current Rating: Up to 300 Amps

Switch Type: On/Off, Two-Position

Benefits

This powerful switch offers several key benefits for your vehicle or marine application:

  • Enhanced system flexibility: Seamlessly switch between different voltage requirements.
  • Improved safety: Disconnect your battery when not in use to prevent accidental drain and protect your electrical system.
  • Reliable performance: Withstand high currents and demanding conditions for dependable operation.

Usage

This switch is commonly used in a variety of applications, including:

  • Cars and trucks with dual battery systems
  • Recreational vehicles (RVs) and campers
  • Marine boats and vessels
  • Off-road vehicles

Connect the positive (+) terminal of your battery to one input of the switch, and connect the positive (+) terminal of your load (e.g., starter motor, accessories) to the output terminal. The negative (-) terminal of the battery should be connected directly to the negative (-) terminal of the load.
name: 12V-48V Selector 2 Position On-Off Power Switch 300A Battery Disconnect Cut Off Kill Switch for Car Vehicle RV Marine Boat
description_short:
Take complete control of your power source with this robust 12V - 48V Selector 2 Position On-Off Power Switch. Designed for demanding applications, this heavy-duty switch boasts a powerful 300A rating, ensuring reliable disconnection and safe operation in various vehicles.

  • Two-Position On-Off Design: Easily switch your power on or off with clear tactile feedback.

This durable kill switch is engineered to withstand harsh conditions and provides a secure disconnect, protecting your valuable electrical components. Experience the peace of mind that comes with precise power management.
